<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cabinet Dentaire Dr Exemple — Formule Pro</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.7; }

    /* Demo banner */
    .demo-banner {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 1000;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #4F5BD5, #6366f1);
      color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 10px 16px; font-size: 14px;
    }
    .demo-banner a { color: #fde68a; margin-left: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
    .demo-banner a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* Navbar */
    nav {
      background: #fff; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      padding: 16px 24px; display: flex; align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
    nav .logo { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; color: #4F5BD5; }
    nav .logo span { font-weight: 400; color: #888; font-size: 14px; display: block; }
    nav ul { list-style: none; display: flex; gap: 24px; }
    nav ul li a { text-decoration: none; color: #555; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 500; }
    nav ul li a:hover { color: #4F5BD5; }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F5BD5 0%, #818cf8 50%, #c4b5fd 100%);
      color: #fff; padding: 80px 24px; text-align: center;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 40px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 18px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 28px; opacity: .9; }
    .hero .cta {
      display: inline-block; background: #fff; color: #4F5BD5;
      padding: 14px 36px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none; transition: transform .2s, box-shadow .2s;
    }
    .hero .cta:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.15); }

    /* Feature badges */
    .badges { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 28px; }
    .badge {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.2); backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3); padding: 8px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Sections */
    .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    section { padding: 64px 0; }
    section h2 { font-size: 28px; color: #1e1b4b; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    section .subtitle { text-align: center; color: #666; margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 16px; }

    /* About */
    .about-content { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; color: #555; font-size: 16px; }

    /* Services */
    .services-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 24px;
    }
    .service-card {
      background: #fff; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 28px; transition: transform .25s, box-shadow .25s;
    }
    .service-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(79,91,213,.1); }
    .service-icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .service-card h4 { color: #4F5BD5; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 17px; }
    .service-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #666; }

    /* Team */
    .team-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; }
    .team-card { text-align: center; }
    .team-photo {
      width: 140px; height: 140px; border-radius: 50%; margin: 0 auto 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c4b5fd, #818cf8);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      color: #fff; font-size: 42px; font-weight: 700;
    }
    .team-card h4 { color: #1e1b4b; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .team-card p { font-size: 14px; color: #888; }

    /* Testimonials */
    .testimonials-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; }
    .testimonial {
      background: #f5f3ff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px;
      border-left: 4px solid #4F5BD5;
    }
    .testimonial p { font-style: italic; color: #555; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .testimonial .author { font-weight: 600; color: #4F5BD5; font-size: 14px; }

    /* Contact form */
    .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; }
    .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {
      width: 100%; padding: 12px 16px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px;
      font-family: inherit; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 16px;
      transition: border-color .2s;
    }
    .contact-form input:focus, .contact-form textarea:focus {
      outline: none; border-color: #4F5BD5;
    }
    .contact-form textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }
    .contact-form button {
      background: #4F5BD5; color: #fff; border: none; padding: 14px 36px;
      border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .2s, transform .2s;
    }
    .contact-form button:hover { background: #4338ca; transform: translateY(-1px); }
    .contact-info-block h4 { color: #1e1b4b; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .contact-info-block p { margin-bottom: 8px; color: #555; font-size: 15px; }
    .contact-info-block a { color: #4F5BD5; text-decoration: none; }

    /* Hours */
    .hours-table { width: 100%; max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .hours-table td { padding: 12px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0; font-size: 15px; }
    .hours-table td:first-child { font-weight: 600; color: #4F5BD5; }

    /* Footer */
    footer {
      background: #1e1b4b; color: #c4b5fd; text-align: center;
      padding: 32px 24px; font-size: 14px;
    }
    footer a { color: #fde68a; text-decoration: none; }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 28px; }
      nav ul { display: none; }
      .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Demo Banner -->
  <div class="demo-banner">
    Site de demonstration JADOMI Studio
    <a href="/studio/onboarding/">Decouvrir la formule &rarr;</a>
  </div>

  <!-- Navbar -->
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">Dr Exemple <span>Chirurgien-Dentiste</span></div>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
      <li><a href="#equipe">Equipe</a></li>
      <li><a href="#avis">Avis</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Des soins dentaires d'excellence</h1>
    <p>Le cabinet du Dr Exemple allie technologie de pointe et approche humaine pour un sourire eclatant.</p>
    <a href="#contact" class="cta">Prendre rendez-vous</a>
    <div class="badges">
      <span class="badge">Prise de RDV en ligne</span>
      <span class="badge">Chatbot intelligent</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About -->
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h2>A propos du cabinet</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Un espace dedie a votre bien-etre dentaire</p>
      <div class="about-content">
        <p>Fonde par le Dr Exemple, notre cabinet vous accueille dans un environnement moderne et apaisant. Nous utilisons les dernieres technologies pour vous offrir des soins precis, confortables et durables. Chaque patient beneficie d'un plan de traitement personnalise.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <section id="services" style="background: #faf9ff;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Nos services</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Une gamme complete de soins dentaires</p>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🦷</div>
          <h4>Soins conservateurs</h4>
          <p>Detartrage, traitement des caries et soins preventifs pour maintenir votre sante bucco-dentaire.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🔩</div>
          <h4>Implantologie</h4>
          <p>Remplacement des dents manquantes par des implants fiables et esthetiques.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">😁</div>
          <h4>Orthodontie</h4>
          <p>Gouttieres invisibles et appareils modernes pour un alignement parfait.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">✨</div>
          <h4>Esthetique dentaire</h4>
          <p>Blanchiment professionnel, facettes et couronnes pour un sourire eclatant.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">👶</div>
          <h4>Pedodontie</h4>
          <p>Soins adaptes aux enfants dans un environnement rassurant et ludique.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h4>Parodontologie</h4>
          <p>Traitement des maladies des gencives pour preserver vos dents naturelles.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Team -->
  <section id="equipe">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Notre equipe</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Des professionnels a votre ecoute</p>
      <div class="team-grid">
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo">DE</div>
          <h4>Dr Exemple</h4>
          <p>Chirurgien-Dentiste — Implantologie &amp; Esthetique</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-photo">DA</div>
          <h4>Dr Adjointe</h4>
          <p>Chirurgien-Dentiste — Orthodontie &amp; Pedodontie</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonials -->
  <section id="avis" style="background: #faf9ff;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Avis patients</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Ils nous font confiance</p>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <p>"Un cabinet moderne et un accueil chaleureux. Le Dr Exemple a pris le temps de m'expliquer chaque etape du traitement. Je recommande vivement !"</p>
          <div class="author">— Patient A.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <p>"Tres satisfait de mes gouttieres d'orthodontie. L'equipe est professionnelle et les resultats sont au rendez-vous."</p>
          <div class="author">— Patient B.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contactez-nous</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Prenez rendez-vous ou posez votre question</p>
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <form class="contact-form" onsubmit="event.preventDefault();">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Votre nom" required>
          <input type="email" placeholder="Votre email" required>
          <input type="tel" placeholder="Votre telephone">
          <textarea placeholder="Votre message"></textarea>
          <button type="submit">Envoyer le message</button>
        </form>
        <div class="contact-info-block">
          <h4>Informations</h4>
          <p><strong>Adresse :</strong> Cabinet de demonstration</p>
          <p><strong>Telephone :</strong> <a href="tel:">XX XX XX XX XX</a></p>
          <p><strong>Email :</strong> <a href="mailto:demo@jadomi.fr">demo@jadomi.fr</a></p>
          <h4 style="margin-top: 28px;">Horaires</h4>
          <table class="hours-table">
            <tr><td>Lun — Jeu</td><td>09h00 — 18h00</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Vendredi</td><td>09h00 — 17h00</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Samedi</td><td>Sur rendez-vous</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Dimanche</td><td>Ferme</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Cabinet Dentaire Dr Exemple &middot; Cabinet de demonstration</p>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px;">Propulse par <a href="/">JADOMI IA</a></p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
